Introduction

IKnow, also known as Ara, is a South Korean singer and dancer under Midas Entertainment. She is a former member of the girl group Astell, the pre-debut girl group Berryz, the girl groups Ndear, and Daydream, and the dance teams ZERO and Babys. She is also a former pre-debut member of the girl group N-DAY.
